---
// Coverage Component
---

<section class="py-24 bg-secondary text-white overflow-hidden" id="cobertura">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-extrabold mb-8">Nuestra Red Nacional</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg mb-10 leading-relaxed">
          Contamos con una infraestructura de rutas consolidada que nos permite conectar los principales polos económicos de Chile, garantizando puntualidad tanto en la pampa nortina como en los fiordos australes.
        </p>
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center text-primary">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined" aria-hidden="true">pin_drop</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-bold">Norte Grande</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Arica, Iquique, Antofagasta, Copiapó, Coquimbo</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center text-primary">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined" aria-hidden="true">pin_drop</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-bold">Zona Central</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Santiago, Valparaíso, Talagante (Base de Operaciones)</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center text-primary">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined" aria-hidden="true">pin_drop</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-bold">Zona Austral</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Curicó, Concepción, Puerto Montt, Coyhaique, Punta Arenas</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="relative flex justify-center">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-primary/5 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
        <!-- Chile Map Representation -->
        <div class="relative bg-white/5 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-white/10">
          <div class="text-center mb-6">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-6xl" aria-hidden="true">map</span>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-4">Cobertura Total</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400">De Arica a Punta Arenas</p>
          </div>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-center">
            <div class="bg-white/5 p-4 rounded-lg">
              <p class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-primary">12+</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 uppercase">Ciudades</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white/5 p-4 rounded-lg">
              <p class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-primary">10</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 uppercase">Unidades</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white/5 p-4 rounded-lg">
              <p class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-primary">UF 2.5K</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 uppercase">Seguro</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white/5 p-4 rounded-lg">
              <p class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-primary">24/7</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 uppercase">GPS</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
